io.confluent.ksql.execution.plan

Interface PlanBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    KSPlanBuilder

    public interface PlanBuilder
    A visitor interface for building a query from an execution plan. There is a single visit method for each execution step type (final implementations of ExecutionStep). Implementers typically implement the visit methods by applying the transformation specified in the step to the stream/table(s) returned by visiting the source steps.
